DTSTAMP:20260612T133530Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260626
SUMMARY:Deadline: Prairie Ronde Artist Residency: Summer/Fall 2026 (Michiga
 n)
DESCRIPTION:Prairie Ronde Artist Residency at The Mill at Vicksburg\, a sel
 f-directed residency open to artists across disciplines including film\, v
 ideo and new media. ELIGIBILITY: artists of any discipline\; open worldwid
 e. Apply via the Prairie Ronde application page.\n\nOrganisation: The Mill
  at Vicksburg\nLocation: Vicksburg\, Michigan\, USA (5-6 week on-site resi
 dency\, private housing)\nAward: $2\,000 stipend plus a $500 travel grant 
 and private housing for the 5-6 week residency. Application fee: $25.\nDur
 ation: Five- to six-week residency\n\nMore: https://prairieronde.org/about
 /apply/
